#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduce the number of #includes in &kde; source files"
msgstr "Verlaagt het aantal #includes in de bronbestanden van &kde;"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>file</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>file</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschrijving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> tries to reduce the number of #includes in C+"
"+ source files. Much of it's processing is specific to &kde; sources and so "
"it might not work so well with sources for non-&kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixuifiles</command> probeert het aantal #includes in C++-"
"bronbestanden te verlagen. Deze procedure is specifiek voor KDE-bronnen en "
"het hoeft dus niet goed te werken voor bronnen die niet bij KDE horen."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following problems are identified by <command>fixincludes</command>:"
msgstr ""
"De volgende probleemgevallen kunnen gevonden worden door "
"<command>fixuifiles</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Including headers that are no longer supported but which exist for "
"compatibility with older Qt/KDE versions;"
msgstr ""
"Ingevoegde headers die niet langer meer ondersteund worden, maar enkel "
"bestaan om oudere Qt/KDE-versies te ondersteunen;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the same file multiple times."
msgstr "Het invoegen van dezelfde header in hetzelfde bestand."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an experimental mode which tries removing each #include one at "
"a time (with a few exceptions) to see whether the source still compiles. "
"Note that this experimental mode will modify the original sources."
msgstr ""
"Er is ook een experimentele modus, welke probeert één voor één een header te "
"verwijderen en controleert of het bestand nog steeds compileert. Opmerking: "
"deze experimentele modus past de originele broncode aan."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the sources will not be modified; the identified problems will "
"simply be written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"De bronbestanden zullen standaard niet aangepast worden, de gevonden "
"probleemgevallen zullen naar de standaard uitvoer geschreven worden."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of C++ sources to examine should be given on the command-line. If "
"no files are given, all C++ sources in or beneath the current directory will "
"be examined (with the exception of directories whose <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> contains <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> or <option>-"
"UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)"
msgstr ""
"De lijst van C++-bestanden dient op de commandoregel opgegeven te worden. "
"Wanneer er geen bestanden gegeven zijn, zullen alle C++-bronnen in de "
"huidige map of in onderliggende mappen gecontroleerd worden (met "
"uitzondering van mappen welke een <filename>Makefile.am</filename> hebben "
"die <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> of <option>-UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option> "
"bevatten)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Dit hulpmiddel is een onderdeel van het software-ontwikkelpakket van &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opties"

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --verbose"
msgstr "-v, --verbose"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verbose mode. Additional debugging output is written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"Veel informatie op standaard uitvoer. Extra debuginformatie zal getoond "
"worden op de standaard uitvoer."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --experimental"
msgstr "-e, --experimental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experimental mode, as described above in detail. Note that this option "
"implies <option>--modify</option>."
msgstr ""
"Experimentele modus, zoals deze hierboven werd beschreven. Deze optie neemt "
"ook automatisch de optie <option>--modify</option> mee."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --modify"
msgstr "-m, --modify"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as writing messages to standard output, actually modify the original "
"sources to fix any problems that were found."
msgstr ""
"Naast het tonen van de uitvoer op de standaard uitvoer, zullen alle "
"probleemgevallen ook meteen opgelost worden in de bronbestanden."

